title: Skidoo (1968) - Otto Preminger (Good Quality)
description:
There were many good, famous actors in Skidoo. 
It starts with Jackie Gleason, and his wife, Carol Channing, at home, watching TV. 

Jackie used to work for the mob. Groucho Marx plays God, a drug dealer who must live on a yacht, hidden in the ocean. There's another guy who is in jail, who has everything and deals from jail. 

Jackie, from the encouragement of God, goes to jail so that he can find and kill the other guy. In jail, Jackie by mistake swallows some LSD. 
Hilarity ensues. 

It is of surprisingly good (OK) quality, compared to the other copies available as torrents. 
This replaces my other copy, that I lost. It is from another computer, same movie. 

Otto Preminger was the director.
